sentences: Gaku Hamada (濱田 岳, Hamada Gaku, born 28 June 1988) is a Japanese film and television actor.
He was a regular cast member of Fuji TV's Operation Love, appearing in all 11 episodes broadcast in 2007 and the 2008 special, and receiving an award for his role.
